    "body": "I would like to raise the current incompatibility between LH and Geth with `TransitionConfigurationV1` before the TTD has been announced.\r\n\r\n- Lighthouse uses [`2**256-2**10`](https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/981b05afb01d5b19be3a5a60ccb12c3582e4c0cf/configs/mainnet.yaml#L15-L16)\r\n- Geth uses `nil`\r\n\r\nI don't really mind what happens here, I would just like to see a standard so that users can start making their nodes merge-ready as soon as possible.",
